{"tid":1010679,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"葵司反擊戰","createTime":"2019-02-06T07:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T04:00:31.000Z","uid":227992,"like":81,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"94dc34c5485ee3f8eb9ee9bbd332a69d6843f1b3","tid":1010679,"uid":227992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"日本尊尼王牌組合嵐宣佈明年底解體發展，隊中的35歲成員松本潤近日再惹是非，有指他的舊相好、AV女優葵司打算出書，公開二人的四年地下情。<br />\n<br />\n松本潤與《花樣男子》拍檔井上真央拍拖多年，不過他在2016年底被爆一腳踏兩船，偷偷地搭上葵司，且關係長達四年。有指松本潤曾威脅葵司，不准她過問有關井上真央的事。做小三的葵司精神狀態一度爆煲，雖然曾向松本潤提出分手，但對方施冧功成功箍煲。兩年前葵司被影到出入松本潤的寓所，複雜關係才得以曝光。近日有消息指葵司對松本潤充滿恨意，決定以舊愛身份出書爆大鑊，不過內容或會包裝成愛情小說形式，此事令松本潤擔心自己形象會直插谷底。<br />\n撰文：哥羅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190206&amp;sec_id=462&amp;s=0&amp;a=20607078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190206%26sec_id%3D462%26s%3D0%26a%3D20607078&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTOvO%2FPyVe1I8S2KINgfvOuE%3D&h=bc8adb70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190206%26sec_id%3D462%26s%3D0%26a%3D20607078&h=740a97d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190206&amp;sec_id=462&amp;s=0&amp;a=20607078</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa4fe19545cf94bfd146d9788f487cfd52a7cbb","tid":1010679,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"我入黎支持葵司唧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18cda6592f81eadab4ee7dc7bd0afde17d597528","tid":1010679,"uid":29929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"支持葵司<br />\n咁卡娃伊比人當性奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67771c1587042b98fb4f9ffe9c620f1e4c108491","tid":1010679,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"葵司整完無咁可愛<i